name: AlignExtensions
desc: Extension methods for the Widget class to provide convenient alignment options.

name: alignAtBottomCenter
desc: Aligns the widget at the bottom center of its parent.

name: alignAtBottomLeft
desc: Aligns the widget at the bottom left of its parent.

name: alignAtBottomRight
desc: Aligns the widget at the bottom right of its parent.

name: alignAtCenter
desc: Aligns the widget at the center of its parent.

name: alignAtCenterLeft
desc: Aligns the widget at the center left of its parent.

name: alignAtCenterRight
desc: Aligns the widget at the center right of its parent.

name: alignAtLERP
desc: Aligns the widget at a linear interpolation between two alignments.

name: alignAtTopCenter
desc: Aligns the widget at the top center of its parent.

name: alignAtTopLeft
desc: Aligns the widget at the top left of its parent.

name: alignAtTopRight
desc: Aligns the widget at the top right of its parent.

name: alignXY
desc: Aligns the widget at a specific x and y coordinate within its parent.

returned by InnerLibsLocalizations.of(context).
